ge of Q2>10GeV2. These studies have opened a new means to study the\ntransition of the nucleon wavefunction through backward-angle experimental\nobservables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Dec 2017 18:43:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 15:34:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-12"}
