 from our work:\nreducing branches and instructions, unrolling loops, eliminating unnecessary\ndata type checks and optimizing the binary code with a compiler on a local\nmachine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Dec 2017 00:34:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-12"}
